item.title: About
item.description: About Leo IOT is a project created to measure various real world data such as temperature and air moisture which are collected from sensor boxes placed in the rooms of the school building. The application will display the data on a dashboard and a 3D-Modell.

item.title: Preview
item.description: Preview You can try out the web dashboard and the 3d model which display sensor values and a 3d Model of the School.
